nodes.text: This crest was used by Admiral Trench as his personal symbol.

Trench was known to mark his personal command ships with this crest. It was the crest on the Separatist dreadnaught Invincible that clued Republic Admiral Wullf Yularen in on the identity of his opponent at the Battle of Christophsis in 22 BBY, having seen it before at the Battle of Malastare Narrows.
